caption: couple’a sleepy boys

DeviantArt: https://www.deviantart.com/ajzan-hataru/art/Snufkin-2019-778784178?ga_submit_new=10%3A1546120601

Twitter: https://twitter.com/AJZan1/status/1079138378778591232

I’m curious about upcoming Moominvalley TV series and how it will turn out. From description it looks like that most attention will be on Moomintroll, but clips show that series will be rather faithful to the books.

When it goes to animation I’m mixed. I like the atmosphere, but models, especially when characters don’t move, look like collectable toys. Not to mention I see some inspirations from ‘90 anime, but I’m probably mistaken.

Snufnin’s model looks OK, but his clothes are to bright for my taste. I’m especially looking forward to see how he will be portrayed.

summary: i got some tight new moomin stuff for christmas this year (among other lovely things) and they came with this little ode to...
body:
i got some tight new moomin stuff for christmas this year (among other lovely things) and they came with this little ode to moomin from the company, finlayson:

“Why do we love Moomin products? The Moomin world is fascinating in its mild madness and anarchy. It stirs your senses, shakes you up, delights you and offers a never-ending stream of fresh perspectives. This applies to everyone, regardless of their age or gender.

It is a great honour to be spreading Tove Jansson’s cheerful messages. We sincerely believe that the more that our world resembles Moomin Valley, the better and more tolerant a place it is for all of us to live in.”

i’m gonna cry

summary: there exists a dark timeline, one darker than this one, where the 3D animated Moomins doesn’t look like thisbut like this...
body:
there exists a dark timeline, one darker than this one, where the 3D animated Moomins doesn’t look like this

but like this

because if Tove Jansson didn’t turn down Walt Disney to buy up the franchise, there would only be two options for Moomin: be the gay winnie the pooh or be the white abomination with 3,000 skin pores/hair follicles
